items.name: Face-Mask-Detection
items.description: This project is a Face Mask Detection system built using computer vision and deep learning techniques. It automatically detects whether a person is wearing a face mask or not in real-time using a webcam or image input.  The main goal of this project is to help enforce health and safety measures in public places by identifying people
